data.description: NEW PRICE !!! Brick ranch in the Brookville School district!! Neat,clean brick 1-story home on a nice level lot w/a metal carport & a 1 car garage.The main level offers a light, bright living room w/fireplace (TV remains),kitchen w/ all appliances (Range, dishwasher, refrigerator, microwave), a  breakfast bar, a dining area w/ a built-in china cabinet (dining area windows overlook the rear yard), a full ceramic-tiled hall bath,2 bedrooms & the master bedroom w/ 2 closets & a full ceramic-tiled bath.There are hardwood floors throughout the main level (hardwood under the carpets in the bdrms). There is also a large enclosed sun porch off the kitchen area.The terrace level includes a large den w/fireplace,laundry room,an oversized 1 car garage with an electric opener & a large unfinished area w/ a roughed-in bath. Within the last 6 months, the entire interior was painted & the chimney was cleaned, sealed & capped.The furnace was just serviced & the septic tank was just pumped.
